        "A Cross-Granularity Chunking Framework\n Authors:Wenxuan Zhang, Yuan-Hao Jiang, Yang Cao, Yonghe Wu View a PDF of the paper titled FreeChunker: A Cross-Granularity Chunking Framework, by Wenxuan Zhang and 3 other authors\n View PDF\n HTML (experimental)\n\n \n Abstract:Chunking strategies significantly impact the effectiveness of Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) systems. Existing methods operate",
